<li><a href="http://electronics.howstuffworks.com/lithium-ion-battery.htm" class="external text" title="http://electronics.howstuffworks.com/lithium-ion-battery.htm" rel="nofollow">How Lithium-ion Batteries Work</a>.</li>
<li><a href="http://news-service.stanford.edu/news/2008/january9/nanowire-010908.html" class="external text" title="http://news-service.stanford.edu/news/2008/january9/nanowire-010908.html" rel="nofollow">Stanford's nanowire battery holds 10 times the charge of existing ones</a>, Stanford Report, <i>December 18, 2007</i></li>
<li><a href="http://www.e-articles.info/e/a/title/The-Lithium-Ion-Battery/" class="external text" title="http://www.e-articles.info/e/a/title/The-Lithium-Ion-Battery/" rel="nofollow">The Lithium Ion Battery</a>.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.e-articles.info/e/a/title/Advantages-and-Limitations-of-the-Lithium-Polymer-Battery/" class="external text" title="http://www.e-articles.info/e/a/title/Advantages-and-Limitations-of-the-Lithium-Polymer-Battery/" rel="nofollow">Advantages and Limitations of the Lithium Polymer Battery</a>, Jan 2007.</li>
</ul>
<p><br /></p>
